social_posts.post_text: We pride ourselves in serving Northeast Florida the best burgers and fries that money can buy. So it should come to no surprise when @duval_bassani says let’s combine the two that’s what we do! Cue the Hamburger Fries 🍔🍟 A generous portion of our Idaho potatoes smothered in cheese sauce, grilled onion, bacon, pink sauce, mustard, topped with delicious sweet pickles and you can’t forget the @certifiedangusbeef patty. It’s the best of both worlds and it’s only at Carolina Jax.. that’s where it’s at! Visit us in Riverside or online at carolinajax.com

Give the gift of delicious burgers this holiday season with a Carolina Jax digital gift card 🎁🎄 The burger lover in your life will be filled with cheer while holding one of our award winning burgers.. like this Patty Melt! Northeast Florida’s original Patty Melt with American cheese, grilled onions and classic sauce on buttery Texas Toast. We are setting the bar for burgers in these parts so get on down and discover why Carolina Jax is where it’s at! 🎁 Purchase your gift card today at carolinajax.com

Line em up Jacksonville! We have one week left until Christmas break so come get it while it’s hot 🍔 Carolina Jax will be closed 12/24 until 01/03 for a much needed break. Our amazing team has been slinging burgers all year and they deserve a break. Don’t worry though, our passion to serve y’all the best burgers in Jacksonville never rests ❤️ We have some exciting new things coming your way in the beginning of the year. Store number 2 opening in Charlotte and a game changer coming to YOU Duval. It’s all in the way that we say.. Carolina Jax is where it’s at! Visit us in Riverside or online at carolinajax.com

Merry Christmas y’all and Happy Holidays 🎄 Carolina Jax will be CLOSED tomorrow 12/24 and reopen on 01/03. Our team has worked very hard all year to serve y’all the best burgers in Northeast Florida and they deserve a (paid) break! It’s about family and giving this time of year and being thankful for the amazing people in your life ❤️ Don’t worry we will be open all day today serving y’all some delicious food. Don’t forget to snag a gift card on our website for you last minute shoppers, yes I’m looking at you. And get on down to Carolina Jax.. that’s where it’s at! Visit us in Riverside or online at carolinajax.com

This New Year resolve to be a better foodie and eat at Carolina Jax! What does eating better mean to us? It means knowing where our ingredients come from. It means not accepting anything less than the best in quality. From the Florida fresh produce, to the @certifiedangusbeef , to the @villagebreadandbagels buns we care what goes into our craft. It means skipping the fast food line and coming on down for some local homegrown goodness 🍔 Swing by today and get your hands on a delicious Charleston. Baby arugula, pimento cheese, bourbon bacon jam, sriracha curry ketchup and a fried egg make this a delectable, dignified southern burger masterpiece. New Year same great burgers.. it’s no wonder why Carolina Jax is where it’s at! Visit us in Riverside or online at carolinajax.com

Can we get a Duuuval?! The Jags are on a winning streak and you can be too when you grab one of our award-winning burgers 🍔 What better way to warm up on a cool day than with our all new Hurricane! White American, white cheddar mac, grilled jalapeño, crumbled bacon and spicy chipotle, it’s sure to heat things up a little bit. Your tailgate party just moved over to Carolina Jax.. tell your friends that’s where it’s at! Visit us in Riverside or online at carolinajax.com 🏈 Go Jags!

This ain’t Waffle House but you can still eat like a pro with one of our award winning burgers 🏈 Try one of @joshallen_41 favorite burgers the Tar Heel today! Roasted poblano mayo, juicy pork, bacon, gold sauce and an onion ring to top it all off. You can be a winner too with one of these award winners in hand 🍔 The Jags have a real shot at victory this season. Support the home team by supporting local. Carolina Jax is where it’s at. Visit us in Riverside or online at carolinajax.com

Get your hands on the best burgers in Northeast Florida with Carolina Jax 🍔 Did you know that we have won more awards than any other burger joint in Jacksonville over the past 10 years?! Our persistent dedication to the craft has gained us national recognition for these hand-pattied hand-smashed pieces of perfection. We use only the finest ingredients including @certifiedangusbeef the best beef money can buy 🥩 One taste and you’ll understand why Carolina Jax is where it’s at! Visit us in Riverside or online at carolinajax.com

NEW MENU ALERT 🚨 We will be dropping our new menu soon and we have kicked the flavor up a notch with our house-made spicy chipotle sauce 🤤 You can get it on a few offerings like this Hurricane! @certifiedangusbeef patty topped with white American, grilled jalapeño, white cheddar mac, crumbled bacon and spicy chipotle sauce. You can get this NOW as a special 🍔 We will also be closing early tomorrow at 4 o’clock so our team can catch the big game! Get your burgers all today and tomorrow from 12-4. So much flavor so many reasons why Carolina Jax is where it’s at! Visit us in Riverside or online at carolinajax.com

NEW MENU ALERT 🚨 Our new menu has officially dropped with some cool new additions like this datil strawberry flavored, you guessed it, milk shake! FINALLY Carolina Jax has shakes 🥤 We are using the finest mix we can find made exclusively by @moxicecream it’s a euro-style ice cream bliss. There are some other fun flavors to discover like maple bacon, peanut butter chocolate, turtle and Oreo to name a few 😋 As we all know the economic hardships are hitting everyone extra hard right now. You may notice a slight restructuring of our menu. In order for us to stay competitive it’s what must be done. If the markets come back down we will readjust things but don’t sweat it the increases are insignificant. Come on down and check out the burger joint that everyone is talking about.. Carolina Jax is where it’s at! Visit us in Riverside or online at carolinajax.com

Catch me LIVE tomorrow morning on @rivercitylivetv  @news4jax as I smash it up with @ranceadamsmedia and talk about our exciting new menu 🍔 I’ll be debuting our newest addition among other things so you don’t want to miss it! Don’t forget to tune in tomorrow morning at 11am. Hang out with me and Rance at the studio doing all kinds of foodie stuff 🤪 The show never stops and neither do these wonderful burgers. Carolina Jax is where it’s at! Visit us in Riverside or online at carolinajax.com

GO VOTE TODAY 🇺🇸 At Carolina Jax we celebrate those who exercise their civic duties. Show your sticker for a $10 lunch special all day TODAY ONLY!! It don’t matter what you stand for as long you stand for something 💪🏻 Voting is how we continue to be named the best burgers in Northeast Florida and beyond. We love this city. Show it the same kind of love and support as you do our burgers ❤️ Join the club. Even Miami knows Carolina Jax is where it’s at. Visit us in Riverside or online at carolinajax.com

What’s better than getting the best lunch combo in Jacksonville? Adding bacon to it 🤤 Add delicious thick cut applewood smoked bacon to practically anything on the menu for just a couple bucks. If there’s one thing we know how to do it’s makin the bacon and we make A LOT! Over 400 pounds a week to be exact. That sweet swine gets the same treatment as our delicious @certifiedangusbeef and that’s cooked fresh every day 🥓 Taste the beauty in simplicity and swing by for a lunch combo TODAY! Burgers, bacon and a belly full of joy.. that’s what makes Carolina Jax where it’s at! Visit us in Riverside or online at carolinajax.com

Miami!!! Tonight is the night. Put your stretchy pants on and come try some amazing burgers from the best of the best 🍔 We won this competition back in 2019 and hope to seal the deal once more. If you’ve tried us at any of our previous events in South Florida you know that you’re in for a treat. @burgerbeast always puts together the best events with unlimited burgers, beer, live music and more. Come show some support because even Miami knows.. Carolina Jax is where it’s at! Visit us in Riverside or online at carolinajax.com

Here it is. Our pièce de résistance. The sweet, the spicy, the savory, the all encompassing, all star award winning Riverside 🍔 We are going through some renovations and will be CLOSED this Easter Sunday until Saturday April 15th ‼️ Come get your burger fix NOW and check out the major upgrades when we get back at it next Saturday. As we continue to grow we want an image conducive with our brand and slowly but surely we are getting there. Please excuse us as we prepare for these exciting renovations and quite possibly the coolest wall art in the city of Jacksonville 🤫 It won’t happen overnight but with your continued support.. we’re making Carolina Jax where it’s at! Visit us in Riverside or online at carolinajax.com

LAST CALL FOR HAMBURGERS 🚨 Come see the first part of our new construction today! This massive neon sign hung in @burgerbeast Burger Museum for years before finding its new home here in Riverside. Made sometime in the 1940’s, it spent most of its life attracting hungry patrons to a burger stand out in Ohio 🍔 Our vision is to recreate these quaint little burger stands that used to litter the cities and highways and helped to shape America into what it is today. As we continue construction towards our goal we have to do things like close shop for the next week 😢 Sorry but we will be CLOSED starting tomorrow and reopen next Saturday 4/15 with a fresh new look. Come discover what Northeast Florida’s best burger joint has to offer. Dedication to excellence is what makes Carolina Jax where it’s at! Visit us in Riverside or online at carolinajax.com

WE’RE BACK OPEN FOR BUSINESS!! Come by tomorrow and see what we’ve been up to. I know it’s been a long hard week but we have some HUGE improvements and the same delicious burgers y’all have come to expect 🍔❤️ #burger #burgers #foodie #foodporn #burgerporn #cookingchannel #certifiedangusbeef #jacksonville #jax #igersjax #illovejax #jaxrestaurantreviews #yelpjax #jaxfoodie  #onlyinduval #whatsgoodjax #904happyhour #voidlive #riverside #burgerbeastapproved #stufftodoinjax #edibleneflorida #sobewff #jaxfoodtrucks #jaxtruckies #natedoesfood #nomnomjax #foodtrucksof904 #carolinajax

In a few weeks we’re taking these burgers on the road up to Hot-lanta! We have the opportunity to cook alongside some of the best in the game for @burgerbenefit charity for @givingkitchen 🍔 If you don’t know about the organization The Giving Kitchen gives back to restaurant industry workers in need. A lot of us in the industry don’t have benefits like health and dental insurance and that’s where they step in to help. From cancer bills to injuries The Giving Kitchen steps up to help when it matters ❤️ I was tasked with creating my own version of the burger from @netflix new movie The Menu. Just a really well done cheeseburger. It’s what we do every day. Because if there’s one place that does burgers very well.. Carolina Jax is where it’s at! Visit us in Riverside or online at carolinajax.com and if you’re in Atlanta follow @burgerbenefit to get your tickets NOW 🙏🏻

It’s more than just a sign. It’s a testament to what we’re trying to accomplish. For years I begged my friend @burgerbeast for this massive sign hanging in his museum. At the time it was just two pieces of tin. Old, tired and waiting on its time to go. We brought life back into it and gave it a purpose ❤️ I feel that’s what Carolina Jax is trying to accomplish here in Northeast Florida. Jacksonville is home to the original Insta-Burger King but over the years the market has grown stale. Carolina Jax is taking the hamburger by its roots, simplicity in its truest form and rejuvenates, revitalizes the excitement for America’s favorite food. From creations that are imaginative to pure and simple and good.. Carolina Jax is always where it’s at 🍔 Come see how we’re smashing it up. Visit us in Riverside or online at carolinajax.com

Patty, bread, cheese, onion, sauce. Sometimes the simplest ingredients come together for an unforgettable creation 🍔 The patty melt originated on the left coast sometime in the late 1940s. Served with grilled onion and Swiss on rye, the patty melt further validated the hamburger’s claim as America’s favorite sandwich. Although made similar, our patty melt isn’t traditional, it’s better ❤️ Everything we do we do with love and a dedication for the craft. Stop by our little burger joint and discover why Carolina Jax is where it’s at! Visit us in Riverside or online at carolinajax.com

IT’S NATIONAL BURGER MONTH 🍔 Excuse us while we flood your feed over the next several weeks with luscious burger content. There might even be a burger special rolling out shortly but you didn’t hear that from me 🤫 We have expanded seating to provide y’all more places to sit to enjoy our award-winning burgers. Come discover what the rest of  Northeast Florida already knows.. Carolina Jax is where it’s at! Visit us in Riverside or online at carolinajax.com

What’s better than a hot juicy burg? How about Burgs for charity ❤️ @burgerbenefit is partnering with @givingkitchen and some of the biggest names in the industry for a one night exclusive all-star collab burger pop-up 🍔 The Giving Kitchen gives back to restaurant workers in need and it’s something we strongly believe in. I’m very grateful to have been invited to cook alongside these legends and I’m gonna show em all just what Northeast Florida is all about 💪🏻 If you’re in the Atlanta area visit burgerbenefit.com and get your tickets now!!! These bad boys are off menu. Giving back one burger at a time.. that’s why Carolina Jax is where it’s at! Visit us in Riverside or online at carolinajax.com

Ain’t no one trick pony when it comes to burgers around here 🤠 At Carolina Jax our passion for the craft extends beyond your run of the mill. Don’t get me wrong we do simple and we do it well. But we also do this 🍔 Meet the multi-award winning Riverside. Key lime datil aioli, baby spinach, chèvre goat cheese, applewood smoked bacon, orange marmalade and a datil hot sauce drizzle. You ain’t from Duuuval unless you know what so many others have already found out… Carolina Jax is where it’s at! Visit us in Riverside or online at carolinajax.com

If you’ve been following us awhile you might remember the collaboration we did with @twistedokiebbq one time 🤔 It was a food truck rally at Academy Sports on Atlantic and the burger was a combination of what we do best topped with their brisket. TOMORROW ONLY UNTIL SOLD OUT you can get something similar to this 🍔 @certifiedangusbeef patty cooked to perfection smothered in smoked Gouda, topped with sweet and spicy house pickles, candied bacon, bourbon barrel smoked brisket and sweet datil bbq sauce 🤤 Now how’s THAT for a special?! Get it tomorrow before we run out and please don’t forget we will be CLOSED THIS SUNDAY for Mother’s Day. If you didn’t already know.. Carolina Jax is where it’s at! Visit us in Riverside or online at carolinajax.com

Alright y’all. This is a special TODAY ONLY 🚨 Don’t come in asking for modifications it’s a take it or leave it kind of special. I stayed up all night smoking this brisket and let me tell you what… Call it “The Special” 🍔 Sweet and spicy pickle, smoked Gouda, candied bacon, bourbon barrel smoked brisket and sweet datil bbq sauce on a potato bun. It just might be the best thing you will ever eat and it’s here TODAY ONLY! Come see what these burgers are about. Carolina Jax is where it’s at! Visit us in Riverside or online at carolinajax.com

What’s in a name? That which we call a burger by any other word would taste as delicious 🍔 Our burgers are crafted to be what we believe are the very best interpretation of what a burger should be. We smash our patties for the delicious crust, sear and carmelization you can only get from a flat top griddle. We give you more than a 1/3 lb of @certifiedangusbeef which we believe is the perfect meat to bun ratio for a fulfilling meal. Our toppings are fresh and made in house daily. Our buns baked fresh right here in Jacksonville, FL and delivered daily as well. Our commitment to quality can go by many names but the most popular we’ve heard is OMG 🤤 Sometimes silence speaks volumes and it’s hard to concentrate on words with a burger like that in hand. Award winning since 2017 because as they say.. Carolina Jax is where it’s at! Visit us this weekend in Riverside or online at carolinajax.com

PRESALE ALERT 🚨 Tickets to the Burger Beast x Carolina Jax Burger Club Meating are on sale NOW at carolinajax.com 🚨 This is going to be one epic evening full of burgers, beer and good times! Sef is bringing his wildly popular Burger Club on the road for an experience Jacksonville has never seen before. You won’t want to miss this one folks. Monday, June 26th right here at Carolina Jax there will be a secret menu including entrees, sides, desserts and did I mention beer?! You don’t want to miss out on this one. Get your tickets NOW before they sell out at carolinajax.com 🍔 Spreading love one burger at a time. That’s what makes Carolina Jax where it’s at. Visit us in Riverside or online at carolinajax.com

BURGER CLUB MEATING TICKETS ON SALE NOW 🚨 Monday, June 26th Carolina Jax is teaming up with Burger Beast for the very first Burger Club Meating in Jacksonville, FL! This is an experience Jacksonville has never seen before. Get to meet the man, the myth and the legend himself and talk all things burgers while experiencing a secret menu for two 🍔 As of now there are only a handful of tickets left so DON’T WAIT! Order now online by visiting carolinajax.com (ticket price is for TWO people) 🍔 Bringing South Florida to North Florida for an experience like no other. Food, beer, desserts and good time. It’s no wonder why Carolina Jax is where it’s at! Visit carolinajax.com for tickets NOW

It’s National Burger Day! Come celebrate with Jacksonville’s OG Smash Bros 🍔 If you’re looking for the best burgers in Jacksonville this weekend then look no farther. We got it right here. Try something fresh like this OBX, our spin on a west coast classic bacon avocado ranch 🏄🏻‍♂️ We still have a few tickets left for our secret menu pop up next month so don’t miss out! Serving y’all the best burgers since 2017. That’s why Carolina Jax is where it’s at. Visit us in Riverside or online at carolinajax.com

It should come as no surprise that our burgers are special 🍔 I’m not talking “everyone is special in their own way” special. Im talking verrrrry special. Just how special? Well they have been named the best burgers in Northeast Florida for the past several years.. But you want to know what makes this pictured burger EXTRA special?! It’s on our weekday lunch special from 11-2 😉 We still have a few tickets left to our Burger Club Meating Monday, June 26th. Visit carolinajax.com now to snag one of the last couple of spots. Just like our burgers, it will be a special experience that any burger lover would enjoy. Please note ticket prices are for TWO. You can’t beat that kind of deal. Special burgers from a special place.. Carolina Jax is where it’s at. Visit us in Riverside or online at carolinajax.com

At Carolina Jax we do smash burgers a little different. Unlike those other smash burger joints we believe in giving you more 🍔 More @certifiedangusbeef over 1/3lb to be exact. Our proprietary smash technique gives you the best of both worlds. A thick juicy patty with that irresistible crust and lacy edges. A higher meat to bun ratio gives you more of that delicious burger flavor in every single bite. We don’t skimp on sides either. More No. 1 Idaho potatoes means a more fulfilling meal. No one leaves hungry 🤤 There’s more to discover at Carolina Jax because we don’t stop delivering. Smashing patties for your pleasure since 2016. Carolina Jax is where it’s at! Visit us in Riverside or online at carolinajax.com

What an amazing day today with @clarawhitemission and Miracle on Ashley Street 🤩 Councilwoman @jucobypittman put on such an amazing event and I am very honored to have been invited to be a part of it. I chopped up some fresh Carolina Q for all in attendance and got to share some laughs and fun times with the wonderful people of Jacksonville 🐷 It’s not only an honor but a privilege to be able to give back to the wonderful city that continues to show us all of their love and support. Thank you Duuuval for helping to make Carolina Jax where it’s at. Visit us in Riverside or online at carolinajax.com

🚨 WE WILL BE CLOSED THIS SUNDAY FOR FATHER’S DAY 🚨 I’d like to give a special shout-out to all of the real fathers out there who are making better lives for their children and their families. I feel dads can be under appreciated at times but not here. We will be closed THIS SUNDAY so the amazing fathers on our team can spend the day being appreciated by the ones they love ❤️ Burgers are great. This OBX pictured being one of them. But family is better. Show dad you care with a Carolina Jax gift card available on our website. Family, food and good intentions.. Carolina Jax is where it’s at. Visit us in Riverside or online at carolinajax.com

Now would ya just look at all that bacon 👀 We ain’t just good burgers. I mean yes that is our claim to fame but did you know that we also cook up over 500 lbs of bacon a week?! We don’t cheat and throw it in an oven either. I’m talking about griddled bacon strips and hand-cut crumbled fresh applewood smoked delicious 🥓 It should come as no surprise that this BST is every bacon lovers dream. Piled high with 1/3lb of applewood smoked bacon, our signature key lime datil aioli, baby spinach and tomato on fresh local made Texas Toast. It’s what’s for lunch tomorrow and it’s only here. Carolina Jax is where it’s at! Visit us in Riverside or online at carolinajax.com

I can’t begin to thank everyone who showed up to make Jacksonville’s first @burgerbeast Burger Club Meating a success 🍔❤️ I had the opportunity to share a little history and some amazing food with the people who help make this place great. Brisket was the star of my menu with a special homage to Canada and let me tell you about that poutine 🤤 This event was such a success that I will be hosting a few more private dinners thru the end of the year. Don’t miss out on the next one! More details coming soon 😎 Passion for the craft is what makes Carolina Jax where it’s at! Visit us in Riverside or online at carolinajax.com

🇺🇸 HAPPY BIRTHDAY WEEKEND AMERICA 🇺🇸 Y’all definitely chose Carolina Jax as the place to kick off your weekend plans! For those of you who missed out tomorrow is your last chance until after the holiday 😬 We’re all celebrating America’s 247th birthday and Carolina Jax will be CLOSED this Tuesday the 4th. Don’t worry. We have plenty of burgers to get you through. Come on down and discover what a lot of Duval already knows.. Carolina Jax is where it’s at! Visit us in Riverside or online at carolinajax.com

Tired of grilling? Let us handle that for you the rest of the week! Our Tar Heel is everything that is America 🇺🇸 It starts with scratch made roasted poblano mayo. A perfectly cooked CAB patty smothered with sharp cheddar cheese, applewood smoked bacon, bourbon barrel pork smoked for 16 hours and drizzled with Carolina gold sauce and a beer battered onion ring to top things off! It’s a burger for the people 🍔 We are committed to serving you the very best burgers in Northeast Florida and we won’t stop until every face is fed. Burgers you can’t stop dreaming about. That’s why Carolina Jax is where it’s at! Visit us in Riverside or online at carolinajax.com

Three years ago this week we opened our location in Riverside. It was in the midst of a global catastrophe and at times felt like the whole world was burning to the ground. Through those ashes a legendary burger joint arose and is now a standing testament to the resilience of the American foodies 🍔 I present to you the multi award winning TRIPLE Riverside! One patty for each year. I’m not sure the customer who ordered this understood the significance of their order but to me it made perfect sense. Cheers to 3 years Duval! We wouldn’t be here without your continued love and support. Jacksonville is what makes Carolina Jax where it’s at. Visit us in Riverside or online at carolinajax.com

I think it’s about time we ran another SUPER SPECIAL 🐔🚨 This time we’re kickin it up a notch with a Mojo Chicken Philly Melt! Yes yes I know what you’re thinking, “But it’s not a burger?!” Did you know that we marinate our white meat halal chicken for over 24 hours in delicious mojo before grilling it up to perfection on our state of the art griddle! Using that same juicy chicken we chop up some mushroom, onion, poblano and bell pepper blend before smothering it in mayo and white American. And the best part? That local baked Texas Toast griddled up beautifully with herb and garlic-infused olive oil 🍞 It’s a special. It’s special and it’s only here until it’s not! Step out of the box and into Carolina Jax for flavor you won’t find anywhere else. Doing it since 2016.. Carolina Jax is where it’s at! Visit us in Riverside or online at carolinajax.com

HAPPY NATIONAL HOT DOG DAY 🌭🇺🇸 The under appreciated frankfurter doesn’t quite get the recognition it deserves. Overshadowed by it’s All-American counterpart the hamburger, hot dogs are like the Scottie Pippen of the sandwich world. Almost looked at as an accompaniment at backyard barbecues. At Carolina Jax we let our glizzies shine! We’re talking griddled jumbo dogs topped with the same quality toppings and flavors that you’ve come to expect 🐶 Pictured is the first hot dog I ever sold back on the food truck. Made the way Queen Charlotte ate them herself and how Carolinians have been making them for centuries. We call it simply “All the way.” Mustard onion, chili and slaw. Nothing less than perfection is what Carolina Jax is all about. Come see for yourself in Riverside or online at carolinajax.com

Some things are just done. Some things are done well and then some things are done extraordinarily! Our goal at Carolina Jax is not to just give you a good burger, we want to change your whole perspective on what a burger should be 🍔 Our menu takes on classic burger recipes and completely reimagines them to create something uniquely perfect and delicious. Like this Mountain Man 🏔️ It’s an OG that’s been on the menu since day one. It is our take on a chili cheese burger. Utilizing fresh CAB scratch made chili, fresh grilled onion and jalapeños and a southwest roasted poblano mayo for a little flair. With a burger like that it’s no wonder why Carolina Jax is where it’s at! Visit us in Riverside or online at carolinajax.com

NEW MENU ALERT 🚨 It’s about that time that we roll out some new and exciting stuff! So let me present to you the Cinnatoast Crunch Shake 🥤 It’s a churro but it’s not. It’s breakfast but it’s not.
